{"name":"ELA-3-3-ResponseGroupChecklistforOpinion","pages":[{"engine":{"module":"engines/form","payload":{"fieldsets":[{"content":"<h1>Response Group Checklist for Opinion</h1><div class='instructions instructions-callout'><p>Everyone in your Response Group will get a turn to read his or her piece aloud, mark off the checklist, and write down suggestions for revision. To begin, one student in the Response Group should read his or her piece aloud while the other members of the group listen.  After reading, the author should hold the checklist and then ask the other members of the Response Group to respond to each element on the checklist.  The author should write down the suggested revisions. Then it’s the next person’s turn to read aloud. </p></div><div class='scrollable-table-top'><table><thead><tr><th style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Questions to Ask the Writer</p></th><th style='width:12%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes </p></th><th style='width:12%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p></th><th style='width:41%;height:100px;'><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Revision Notes</p></th></tr></thead></table></div><div class='scrollable-table-bottom'><table><tbody><tr><td style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p>Does your opinion piece introduce the topic or text that you are writing about?</p></td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{2-2}}</td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{2-3}}</td><td style='width:41%;height:100px;'>{{2-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p>Is your opinion piece organized with reasons?</p></td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{3-2}}</td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{3-3}}</td><td style='width:41%;height:100px;'>{{3-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p>Does your opinion piece state an opinion and have reasons that support that opinion?</p></td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{4-2}}</td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{4-3}}</td><td style='width:41%;height:100px;'>{{4-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p>Does your opinion piece use linking words to connect opinions and reasons?</p></td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{5-2}}</td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{5-3}}</td><td style='width:41%;height:100px;'>{{5-4}}</td></tr><tr><td style='width:35%;height:100px;'><p>Does your opinion piece provide a concluding statement?</p></td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{6-2}}</td><td style='width:12%;height:100px;'>{{6-3}}</td><td style='width:41%;height:100px;'>{{6-4}}</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","className":"subject-ELA left-header top-header","fields":{"2-2":{"name":"2-2","attr":{"name":"2","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"2-3":{"name":"2-3","attr":{"name":"2","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"2-4":{"name":"2-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"2-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"3-2":{"name":"3-2","attr":{"name":"3","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"3-3":{"name":"3-3","attr":{"name":"3","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"3-4":{"name":"3-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"3-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"4-2":{"name":"4-2","attr":{"name":"4","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"4-3":{"name":"4-3","attr":{"name":"4","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"4-4":{"name":"4-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"4-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"5-2":{"name":"5-2","attr":{"name":"5","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"5-3":{"name":"5-3","attr":{"name":"5","type":"radio","value":"3"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"5-4":{"name":"5-4","attr":{"class":"contenteditable","name":"5-4"},"tagName":"textarea"},"6-2":{"name":"6-2","attr":{"name":"6","type":"radio","value":"2"},"tagName":"input","className":"icon"},"6-3":{"name":"6-3","a